replies.bodyText:
Rather than populating this resource completely in code like this, it seems like it would be simpler to download the file from here, remove the "text" section and save that in the test resources, then load it.
For example:
// ensure ctx is a FhirContext with the correct NarrativeGenerator
IParser parser = ctx.newJsonParser();

// load initial data (this is our "given" for the test)
AllergyIntolerance given = parser.parseResource(AllergyIntolerance.class, getClass().getClassLoader().getResourceAsStream("allergyintolerance-example.json"));

